elements.expression:
essql query="SELECT sourceName FROM \"plant-*\""
| dropdownControl valueColumn="sourceName" filterColumn="sourceName"
| render

filters
| essql query="SELECT ROUND(AVG(values.PreStage), 3) as prestage FROM \"plant-*\""
| math "prestage"
| metric "Average Temperature (F)" 
  metricFont={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=36 align="center" color="#000000" weight="normal" underline=false italic=false} 
  labelFont={font size=14 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center"}
| render

filters
| essql query="SELECT ROUND(AVG(values.MidStage), 3) as midstage FROM \"plant-*\""
| math "midstage"
| metric "Average Temperature (F)" 
  metricFont={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=36 align="center" color="#000000" weight="normal" underline=false italic=false} 
  labelFont={font size=14 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center"}
| render

filters
| essql query="SELECT ROUND(AVG(values.PostStage), 3) as poststage FROM \"plant-*\""
| math "poststage"
| metric "Average Temperature (F)" 
  metricFont={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=36 align="center" color="#000000" weight="normal" underline=false italic=false} 
  labelFont={font size=14 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center"}
| render

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT \"@timestamp\" as time,  ROUND(values.PreStage,3) as current_temp FROM \"plant-*\" ORDER BY time DESC LIMIT 1"
| math "current_temp"
| progress shape="verticalPill" 
  font={font size=24 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center"} max=200 label=true valueWeight=40 barWeight=40
| render

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT \"@timestamp\" as time,  ROUND(values.MidStage,3) as current_temp FROM \"plant-*\" ORDER BY time DESC LIMIT 1"
| math "current_temp"
| progress shape="verticalPill" 
  font={font size=24 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center"} max=200 label=true valueColor="#1785b0" barWeight=40 valueWeight=40
| render

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT \"@timestamp\" as time,  ROUND(values.PostStage,3) as current_temp FROM \"plant-*\" ORDER BY time DESC LIMIT 1"
| math "current_temp"
| progress shape="verticalPill" 
  font={font size=24 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center"} max=200 label=true valueColor="#f5cc5d" valueWeight=40 barWeight=40
| render

filters
| demodata
| markdown "### Current Temperature (F)"
| render
